content.description: Steam cleaning and disinfecting of the bathroom in its totality. Provision of fresh towels.
Taking care of general gardening to provide an immaculate first impression
Cleaning and streak removal of external windows
Car wash including vacuum
Provision of laundry services by removal of laundry and return of laundry. Includes a surcharge for delivery.
Provision of laundry services making use of client's machines. Note that where this has been booked, but machines are not available, this will automatically be adjusted to offsite laundry services.
Maintain your upholstery (chair, couch and seat) in pristine condition. We use only the most delicate clearning methods.
General cleaning of living room, returning the room to its immaculate state.
Wall washing to remove marks and cob webs
Steam cleaning and disinfecting of mattresses
Cleaning of pool, including chemical treatments, sweeping and proper flush.
General bedroom cleaning, rubbish removal, bed making, etc.
Cleaning and servicing of braai and reception areas
Deep cleaning of kitchen appliances to remove grease, grime and spills or other marks. Includes ovens, burners, fridges and microwaves.
General cleaning of dining room, returning the room to its immaculate state.
Dishwashing, general kitchen cleaning, cleaning of cookers and hobs.
Cleaning to remove stains and deep seated dirt.
Proper washdown, dusting and cleaning of cabinets
Cleaning and streak removal of internal windows
Deep cleaning to restore not-so-obvious spaces by dusting / cleaning / removing marks on spaces like light fittings, fans, blinds and shutters.
Polishing and waxing of all types of floors, incl. wooden, concrete and stone.
